# Agent Autonomy Guard
# 
# Patterns for directories that autonomous agents MUST NOT access.
# Human-led collaboration may override by explicitly referencing specific files.
#
# Usage: Tools that scan, index, or retrieve content should exclude these patterns
# when operating autonomously. Human-directed sessions may access these paths
# when the human explicitly points to specific files.
#
# See: .workspace/START.md → "Visibility & Autonomy Rules"

# Human-led scratchpad (persistent thinking/research)
.workspace/.scratch/**

# Human-led inbox (temporary staging for imports)
.workspace/.inbox/**

# Human documentation (never agent-accessible)
.workspace/.humans/**

# Deprecated content (never agent-accessible)
.workspace/.archive/**
